"use client"

import {
  BookOpen,
  CreditCard,
  Settings,
} from "lucide-react"
import "./Content.css"
import Dashboard from "./Dashboard/Dashboard"
import UserManagement from "./UserSection"
import OrdersManagement from "./OrderSection"
import DashboardSection from "./Dashboard/DashboardSection"
import MenuManager from "./MenuManager"

const Content = ({ selectedPage }) => {

    switch (selectedPage) {
        case "dashboard":
          return <Dashboard />
        case "user":
          return <UserManagement />
        case "menu":
          return <MenuManager icon={<BookOpen className="h-5 w-5" />} />
        case "order":
          return <OrdersManagement />
        case "payment":
          return <DashboardSection title="Payment Management" icon={<CreditCard className="h-5 w-5" />} />
        case "settings":
          return <DashboardSection title="Settings" icon={<Settings className="h-5 w-5" />} />
        default:
          return <Dashboard />
    }
}

export default Content
